        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/c/a183cd/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2020-01-13T00:12:55.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I don\u2019t know much about Burgundy either but I do dabble in it. I myself would be interested in any books if others have recommendations.</p>\n<p>These two topics for me have been very educational:</p><aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\" data-onebox-src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=1&amp;t=155013&amp;hilit=1000\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/original/3X/e/8/e87148ebcd1df56551c495d1105f732d10f7da42.png\" class=\"site-icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=1&amp;t=155013&amp;hilit=1000\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"06:51AM - 16 October 2018\">WineBerserkers \u2013 16 Oct 18</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <img src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db3686/original/1X/973cca6246737ae55b5ad7fbc6bddc245f0ca306.png\" class=\"thumbnail onebox-avatar\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\">\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=1&amp;t=155013&amp;hilit=1000\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Thoughts on Buying and Consuming BURGUNDY</a></h3>\n\n  <p>Quick Intro: I\u2019m quite early on in my wine buying and drinking career and have already found myself entranced with Burgundy. It seems to be arguably the most intellectually stimulating region and I love the taste of the wines. I\u2019ve been fortunate to...</p>\n\n  <p>\n    <span class=\"label1\">Reading time: 70 mins \ud83d\udd51</span>\n      <span class=\"label2\">Likes: 18 \u2764</span>\n  </p>\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n<aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\" data-onebox-src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=1&amp;t=162364\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/original/3X/e/8/e87148ebcd1df56551c495d1105f732d10f7da42.png\" class=\"site-icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=1&amp;t=162364\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"05:49PM - 24 July 2019\">WineBerserkers \u2013 24 Jul 19</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <img src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db3686/original/1X/973cca6246737ae55b5ad7fbc6bddc245f0ca306.png\" class=\"thumbnail onebox-avatar\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\">\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=1&amp;t=162364\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">2016 Hubert Lignier Morey St Denis 1er VV - best sub $200 burgundy out there?</a></h3>\n\n  <p>In the past few months I\u2019ve had the 2001, 2006, 2008, 2014, 2015, 2016 Hubert Lignier Morey St Denis 1er VV and they\u2019ve all been glorious burgundy shooting way past their price point of $170-200. The last few vintages have been utterly spectacular as...</p>\n\n  <p>\n    <span class=\"label1\">Reading time: 31 mins \ud83d\udd51</span>\n      <span class=\"label2\">Likes: 2 \u2764</span>\n  </p>\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n",
