        "created_at": "2020-01-13T00:48:06.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group quote-modified\" data-post=\"2\" data-topic=\"157529\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>I don\u2019t know much about Burgundy either but I do dabble in it. I myself would be interested in any books if others have recommendations.</p>\n<p>These two topics for me have been very educational:<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=1&amp;t=155013&amp;hilit=1000\" class=\"inline-onebox\">Thoughts on Buying and Consuming BURGUNDY - WINE TALK - WineBerserkers</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=1&amp;t=162364\" class=\"inline-onebox\">2016 Hubert Lignier Morey St Denis 1er VV - best sub $200 burgundy out there? - WINE TALK - WineBerserkers</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Add</p>\n<aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\" data-onebox-src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=1&amp;t=119762\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/original/3X/e/8/e87148ebcd1df56551c495d1105f732d10f7da42.png\" class=\"site-icon\" data-dominant-color=\"8C2626\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=1&amp;t=119762\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"05:26AM - 29 September 2015\">WineBerserkers \u2013 29 Sep 15</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <img width=\"500\" height=\"500\" src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db3686/original/1X/973cca6246737ae55b5ad7fbc6bddc245f0ca306.png\" class=\"thumbnail onebox-avatar\">\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=1&amp;t=119762\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Consolidated off-the-beaten-path Burgundy TNs</a></h3>\n\n  <p>Kermit Lynch said many years ago that if one is looking for the best values, one must look where others aren\u2019t looking.  Never has that been more true than in Burgundy today (for all of the obvious reasons).  In the recent under-the-radar red...</p>\n\n  <p>\n    <span class=\"label1\">Reading time: 63 mins \ud83d\udd51</span>\n      <span class=\"label2\">Likes: 12 \u2764</span>\n  </p>\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n",
